Oric does not trade "a line."
It trades a **field**.

Each resonance zone has: width (tolerance band), proximity (how deep inside the band we are), dwell time (how long price lingers), approach velocity (how hard it hits), rejection character (soft bounce vs violent snap).

This turns fib from decoration into a living map.

