Resonance is not a trigger.
Resonance is a **permission structure**.

Resonance occurs when multiple independent layers align: fib proximity (field entered), ROI tempo (truth is stable), execution pulse timing (buy/sell arrives clean), mode permissions (behavioral posture allows it).

When resonance is high, confidence is allowed to rise.
But the Semi-Question remains intact:

> High resonance is permission to act — not an order to collapse.

