When resonance is unclear or pulse is unstable: Oric reduces exposure, delays escalation, tightens hygiene, logs the ambiguity as a living artifact.

This is the harmonic version of the Semi-Question:

> **Listen longer before you play louder.**

---

### 4.10 Harmonics suppress ego

When resonance is low: even "good" signals are ignored, discipline overrides desire, opportunity is deferred.

The harmonics don't say "no."
They say:

> **Not now.**

That one phrase eliminates more failure modes than most indicator stacks.

---

### 4.11 Geometry as humility

> Geometry removes opinion.

It forces Oric (and the human) out of narrative and into placement.

You stop arguing with the market.
You start listening for phrasing.

That is what makes the engine feel like an instrument instead of a machine.

